data.description: You dream home is waiting for you! This 3 BR 2 BA split level home has fresh interior and exterior paint, new carpets, custom cabinets, and a up to date HVAC that has been serviced . Discover a bright and open interior with plenty of natural light and a neutral color palette, complimented by a fireplace. Enjoy the dining area and the kitchen is ready for cooking with SS appliances that include a refrigerator along with ample counter space and cabinets for storage. The owners suite is serene and comes with a spacious walk in closet and and a relaxing primary bathroom . Extra bedrooms add nice flex space for your everyday needs. The back yard is the perfect spot to kick back. Minutes from downtown Decatur, major highways, and popular recreation offerings- this home is ideal for someone wanting a great deal . Don't miss this incredible opportunity.
